[div class=p 
	[b 
		"Obtaining the swf
	]b
	":
	$LF
	"First of all, these instructions only apply on Windows. I'm not sure how/if it's possible to do this on Linux.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"You will need a copy of The Binding of Isaac and the Wrath of the Lamb expansion on Steam. Install it and run it. 
	$LF
	"While it's running, go to path\to\AppData\Local\Temp. There should be a folder starting with "wrd-" followed by random numbers and letters. In there, there will be ~swd1.dat, ~swd1.swf, and 4 numbered .mdd files. ~swd1.dat is the swf file, simply rename it to change the extension.
	$LF
]div
